  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/6d84654d096752268f53d7c6fb3e77a0.webp?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=63 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"Oh you who enter, abandon all hope\"</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/2306c4d151909d1e545b55ed026ee94e.poster.avif?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/2306c4d151909d1e545b55ed026ee94e.webm?t=1758942513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/2306c4d151909d1e545b55ed026ee94e.mp4?t=1758942513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/6d84654d096752268f53d7c6fb3e77a0.webp?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=63 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HISTORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sheol Inferno is a roguelike card game based on Dante's Divine Comedy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will accompany Dante on his journey through the 9 circles of Hell and fight alongside him to defeat the guardians of the circles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/98a6a89a282b4b2ba9c5afb947778d00.poster.avif?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/98a6a89a282b4b2ba9c5afb947778d00.webm?t=1758942513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/98a6a89a282b4b2ba9c5afb947778d00.mp4?t=1758942513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/6d84654d096752268f53d7c6fb3e77a0.webp?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=63 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME MODE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the cards from the Spanish deck or Poker deck  to complete the missions that will be assigned to you in each circle and thus be able to access the next one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/a05d79b8ce8a035f252714c54f67a0e1.poster.avif?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/a05d79b8ce8a035f252714c54f67a0e1.webm?t=1758942513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/a05d79b8ce8a035f252714c54f67a0e1.mp4?t=1758942513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/6d84654d096752268f53d7c6fb3e77a0.webp?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=63 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ROGUELIKE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the game you will earn gold that will allow you to obtain Blessings to help you on your adventure and, at the end of the game, you will be able to improve your skills on your character sheet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/fca960a493784473eb513adf4a984a0c.poster.avif?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/fca960a493784473eb513adf4a984a0c.webm?t=1758942513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/fca960a493784473eb513adf4a984a0c.mp4?t=1758942513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/6d84654d096752268f53d7c6fb3e77a0.webp?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=63 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card roguelike.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spanish deck of cards or Poker deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deck Management.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on the lore of the Divine Comedy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highly replayable.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NO micro transactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will be translated to Español, English and Italian</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367770/extras/dcef132d1ad94fe19bdb9a7690681a62.poster.avif?t=1758942513\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea